          "topic_refs": [],
          "atoms": [],
          "speaker": "B"
        },
        {
          "id": "sent.ja-a1-r250-dialogue-restaurant-002.t05",
          "surface": "A: お茶をください。",
          "vocab_refs": [],
          "topic_refs": [],
          "atoms": [],
          "speaker": "A"
        },
        {
          "id": "sent.ja-a1-r250-dialogue-restaurant-002.t06",
          "surface": "B: かしこまりました。少々お待ちください。",
          "vocab_refs": [],
          "topic_refs": [],
          "atoms": [],
          "speaker": "B"
        },
        {
          "id": "sent.ja-a1-r250-dialogue-restaurant-002.t07",
          "surface": "A: すみません、お水もお願いします。",
          "vocab_refs": [],
          "topic_refs": [],
          "atoms": [],
          "speaker": "A"
        },
        {
          "id": "sent.ja-a1-r250-dialogue-restaurant-002.t08",
          "surface": "B: はい、すぐお持ちします。",
          "vocab_refs": [],
          "topic_refs": [],
          "atoms": [],
          "speaker": "B"
        },
        {
          "id": "sent.ja-a1-r250-dialogue-restaurant-002.t09",
